topRight.name: Secure Leadership Partnership
topRight.subtitle: Ideal Marriage
topRight.description: Strong husband, strong wife, clear roles, deep affection, spiritual unity, sexual safety, emotional truth.
topRight.biblicalFrame: Mutual submission under God, different roles, same worth.

topLeft.name: Codependent / Enmeshed
topLeft.subtitle: High Closeness, Low Differentiation
topLeft.description: I need you to need me. Fear of conflict, loss of polarity, often low attraction.
topLeft.warning: Feels safe but erodes identity and desire.

bottomRight.name: Authoritarian / Abusive
bottomRight.subtitle: Control Without Intimacy
bottomRight.description: Control, fear, compliance without intimacy, spiritual or emotional coercion.

bottomLeft.name: Detached / Avoidant
bottomLeft.subtitle: Roommates
bottomLeft.description: No pursuit, no polarity, no emotional risk, dead bedroom energy.
bottomLeft.warning: Marriage is dying. Urgent intervention needed.

idealZone.description: Confident leadership with high emotional safety
